# Performance mods for Forge 1.20.1

## Highly recommended list

These mods are the most highly tested, stable, and performant mods out there. We recommend adding **all** of these (or relevant alternatives) to modpacks, unless in the extremely rare cases of incompatibilities or issues. In cases of mod issues, report them to the relevant parties' issue tracker.

| Name                                                                                                   | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                | Additional Notes                                                                                                                                                              | License                                                                                                                  | Alternatives                                                                                                                                 |
| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| [Alternate Current](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alternate-current)                    | Vanilla-compatible redstone optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                  | -                                                                                                                                                                             | MIT                                                                                                                      | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Connectivity](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/connectivity)                              | Fix Login timeouts, Packet sizes errors, Payloads errors, ghostblocks and more                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                                                             | All Rights Reserved                                                                                                      | [Packet Fixer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/packet-fixer)                                                                    |
| [Crash Assistant](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/crash-assistant)                        | Shows a GUI after Minecraft crashes, immediately showing and analyzing all affected logs.                                                                                                                                  | Does not improve game performance by itself - instead helps diagnose issues when they do happen                                                                               | [KostromDan's Modded Minecraft License](https://github.com/KostromDan/Crash-Assistant/blob/app-common-config/LICENSE.md) | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Cyanide](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cyanide)                                        | Reduces data pack world generation pain by providing useful, informative error messages.                                                                                                                                   | Does not improve  game performance by itself - instead changes worldgen crash logs to be more readable                                                                        | MIT                                                                                                                      | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Dynamic FPS](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamic-fps)                                | Improve performance when Minecraft is in the background                                                                                                                                                                    | -                                                                                                                                                                             | MIT                                                                                                                      | [FPS Reducer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fps-reducer)                                                                      |
| [Bobby Reforged](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bobby-reforged)                          | Allows for render distances greater than the server's view-distance setting                                                                                                                                                | -                                                                                                                                                                             | GNU LGPL                                                                                                                 | [Farsight](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/farsight), though this mod lacks a chunk caching feature.                            |
