| [FastWorkbench](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fastworkbench)                            | A performance upgrade for the crafting table                                                                                                                                                                               | Adds tooltips to Crafting Tables while the mod is installed. Can be disabled by going to `config/fastbench.cfg` and setting `"Disable tooltip on crafting table"` to `false`. | MIT                                                                                                                      | -                                                                                                                                            |
