| [Modernfix](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/modernfix)                                    | All-in-one mod that improves performance, reduces memory usage, and fixes many bugs                                                                                                                                        | Enabling [Dynamic Resources](https://github.com/embeddedt/ModernFix/wiki/Dynamic-Resources-FAQ) can halve RAM usage                                                           | GNU LGPL                                                                                                                 | -                                                                                                                                            |
